  "texts": [
    "Such versatility enhances its usefulness in visual search, design assistance, and content creation.",
    "Enhanced Language Understanding: Google's expertise in search and machine translation enriches Gemini's language comprehension.",
    "This results in more precise and relevant responses compared to text-focused LLMs.",
    "Energy Efficiency: Gemini prioritizes computational efficiency, outperforming ChatGPT in terms of speed and energy consumption.",
    "This makes it a more economical solution for large-scale applications.Commitment to Openness: There are indications that Google may adopt an open-source model for Gemini, fostering community-driven development and wider accessibility in the AI domain."
